Package crm.oilwhere.repository

package crm.oilwhere.repository
Manages data persistence for the OilWhere CRM application.

This package includes repository interfaces that handle CRUD operations and database interactions. These interfaces typically extend Spring Data JPA or similar frameworks to abstract database access.

  • Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    CustomerRepository
    Repository interface for managing customer entities in the database.
    FilterRepository
    Repository interface for managing filter entities in the database.
    NewsletterRepository
    Repository interface for managing newsletter entities in the database.
    PurchaseRepository
    Repository interface for managing purchase records in the database.
    UserRepository
    Repository interface for managing user entities in the database.
